children.name: Apps Queries
children.description:
event types: app_allow, app_remove, team_app_allow,team_app_remove
time series area chart showing four different events - created 1d / 30 d
list of recent events with details - created 1d

children.name: Apps Events
children.searchQuery:
apps | parse ",*" as json_object
| json field=json_object "event_category", "event_type", "event_type_description", "name", "country", "info_dict", "ip_address"
| where event_category="apps"
| json field=info_dict "name" as app_name
| fields - info_dict, json_object

children.name: Device Events
children.searchQuery:
devices | parse ",*" as json_object
| json field=json_object "event_category", "event_type", "event_type_description", "name", "country", "info_dict", "ip_address"
| where event_category="devices"
| json field=info_dict "display_name", "platform"
| fields - info_dict, json_object

monitors.name: Recent Device Events Location
monitors.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=DropBox3 | parse ",*" as json_object
| json field=json_object "event_category", "event_type_description", "name", "country", "info_dict", "ip_address"
| where event_category="devices"
| json field=info_dict "display_name", "platform"
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = ip_address
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code

monitors.name: Device Events over time
monitors.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=DropBox3 | parse ",*" as json_object
| json field=json_object "event_category", "event_type", "event_type_description", "name", "country", "info_dict", "ip_address"
| where event_category="devices"
| json field=info_dict "display_name", "platform" | timeslice 1h | count _timeslice, event_type | transpose row _timeslice column event_type

monitors.name: Linked a Device
monitors.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=DropBox3 | parse ",*" as json_object
| json field=json_object "event_category", "event_type", "event_type_description", "name", "country", "info_dict", "ip_address"
| where event_category="devices"
| json field=info_dict "display_name", "platform"
| where event_type = "device_link"
| count by name, display_name, event_type_description, country

monitors.name: Successfully deleted files

| where event_type = "delete_on_unlink_success"

monitors.name: Removed a Device

monitors.name: Failed to delete some files
